            "id": 5900719,
            "title": "《異動股》內險股升國壽漲半成,人行重申擇機降準降息A股升1%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社14日專訊》中國平安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02318:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02318\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02318-HK</a>)現價升3.7%,報48.25元;國壽(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02628:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02628\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02628-HK</a>)升4.5%,報16.24元;新華保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01336:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01336\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01336-HK</a>)升5.8%,報29.35元;太保(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02601:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02601\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02601-HK</a>)升5.5%,報25.1元;中國太平(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00966:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00966\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00966-HK</a>)升3.7%,報12.46元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　中國人民銀行黨委召開擴大會議,重申「實施好適度寬鬆的貨幣政策」。會議提出,將根據國內外經濟金融形勢和金融市場運行情況,擇機降準降息,綜合運用公開市場操作等多種貨幣政策工具,保持流動性充裕,使社會融資規模、貨幣供應量增長同經濟增長、價格總水平預期目標相匹配。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報23797,升334點或升1.4%,主板成交超過773億元。國企指數報8816,升175點或升2%。恒生科技指數報5827,升79點或升1.4%。即月期指新報23830,升342點,高水32點。即月國指期貨報8829,升185點,高水13點。即月科指期貨新報5835,升88點,高水8點。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　上證綜合指數報3393,升34點或升1%,成交2609.39億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。深證成份指數報10883,升147點或升1.4%,成交3645.19億元<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/cnyusd\">人民幣</a>。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>中國平安(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02318:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02318\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02318-HK</a>)</td><td>48.25元</td><td>升3.65%</td></tr><tr><td>國壽(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02628:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02628\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02628-HK</a>)</td><td>16.24元</td><td>升4.5%</td></tr><tr><td>新華保險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01336:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01336\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01336-HK</a>)</td><td>29.35元</td><td>升5.77%</td></tr><tr><td>太保(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02601:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02601\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02601-HK</a>)</td><td>25.1元</td><td>升5.46%</td></tr><tr><td>中國太平(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00966:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00966\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00966-HK</a>)</td><td>12.46元</td><td>升3.66%</td></tr><tr><td>眾安在綫(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:06060:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/06060\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">06060-HK</a>)</td><td>12.66元</td><td>升1.28%</td></tr><tr><td>財險(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02328:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02328\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02328-HK</a>)</td><td>13.4元</td><td>升1.06%</td></tr><tr><td>人保(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01339:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01339\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01339-HK</a>)</td><td>4.37元</td><td>升3.07%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(vs)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>",
